\"https://na.cx/i/Hq4GFns.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHq4GFns.jpg&h=8dba42ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在波蘭U20世界盃F組最後一輪比賽，南韓2：1擊敗阿根廷，近6屆5次晉級淘汰賽。將會於香港時間6月4日晚上11時30分與日本會師16強。<br />\n<br />\n其餘16強形勢是哥倫比亞對紐西蘭、烏克蘭對巴拿馬、意大利對波蘭、阿根廷對馬里、法國對美國、烏拉圭對厄瓜多爾和塞內加爾對尼日利亞。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙媒體評選賽事12位新星，有兩名亞洲球員上榜。沙特10號球員Turki Al-Ammar是沙特聯賽表現最好的球員之一。而南韓的李康仁也成功入選，他效力西甲球隊華倫西亞。 今年曾於聯賽及西班牙盃上陣；3月，他還入選有孫興慜領銜的大國腳。<br />\n<br />\n南韓對阿根廷憑李康仁左路傳中，中鋒吳世勳頭鎚領先1球。而下半場鄭洪金左路過人後傳中，曹永旭推射得手2-0。阿根廷6奪世青盃為歷隊最多。本場射門高達23次，南韓僅有7次。 最終有Adolfo Gaich追成1:2，小組兩勝一負排第1位。南韓力壓缺少賓菲加主力Joao Felix的葡萄牙排第2。 <br />\n<br />\n而日本在最後一輪0-0賽和意大利，小組第2出線。當中有18歲前鋒宮代大聖梅開二度大勝墨西哥。日本將力爭自03年再度晉級8強。<br />\n<br />\n早前日本公佈美洲盃名單，效力FC東京的久保建英首次入選大國腳，更成為史上第2年輕的一隊球員。主帥森保一明言有助對方成長。他今季聯賽入4球。早前有消息指，巴塞隆拿有意在他6月4日年屆18歲後重簽對方。<br />\n<br />\n早前中國於熊貓盃3戰全敗後，有球員說過：&ldquo;我們為保存實力才輸給南韓，畢竟我們基本功不差，與他們差距不大。這次沒有進世青盃，也是要保存實力而沒有去。&rdquo; 中國已經連續7屆無緣世青盃，上一次已是2005年。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T10:44:29.000Z","msg":"留足七年力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:45:58.000Z","msg":"阿爾克馬爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a519a67a02510a38be6d5a5356d3b49cbf2dd573","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T03:00:23.000Z","msg":"felix入大國腳<br />\n葡萄牙都喺熱門<br />\n不過炒十二碼出局 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5819067edee7358042ee7584a2ae230a86a7568a","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727db4ab408bdcc864f9107237bf0810c58efb39","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T08:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XyShmcY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXyShmcY.jpg&h=d6e132d2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n久保建英上咗雜誌封面"},{"pid":"9a9f88ec5c2c9c0432c97a365a1b3fd8770b742c","tid":1181082,"uid":253829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T09:25:08.000Z","msg":"可惜無鄭優營<br />\n一個拜仁一個華西青訓"},{"pid":"c124aaf84cf1bdd83c83bea072ebfef67bce1c2c","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"727db4ab408bdcc864f9107237bf0810c58efb39","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T08:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XyShmcY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXyShmcY.jpg&h=d6e132d2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n久保建英上咗雜誌封面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:18:03.000Z","msg":"如果日本無參加美洲盃<br />\n今場睇佢對李康仁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c35b07d4a3ff3cc95f53f6362c17303bc66c33","tid":1181082,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QTVnDub.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTVnDub.jpg&h=48c60780&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e076bd11c2b985955e3ce2b1cc4059b6a6482f27","tid":1181082,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:25:14.000Z","msg":"日本幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0e4dd2bb1fad7aaa4719e786978099352d26c8","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a9f88ec5c2c9c0432c97a365a1b3fd8770b742c","tid":1181082,"uid":253829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T09:25:08.000Z","msg":"可惜無鄭優營<br />\n一個拜仁一個華西青訓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:16:34.000Z","msg":"2隊要打升班戰<br />\n所以唔放 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75d201334a12e30c2b51170448e81ee9a59c289","tid":1181082,"uid":235152,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T10:51:46.000Z","msg":"中國球員稱為保存實力無去,垃圾最鐘意搵借口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4106ccec121920c5aa914dac038f72f864360fe7","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T14:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e01c73a5bb9703c27d54ecafcf353aaed70f417","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:09:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>世青盃撼南韓 日本中堅：嚴防高波</strong><br />\n<br />\n周二世青盃16強爆發亞洲大戰，日本U20硬撼南韓U20，隊長齊藤未月（Mitsuki Saito）賽前先認低威。<br />\n<br />\n日本一眾球員進行1小時高強度練習，以備戰老對手南韓。隊長齊藤未月在記者會上表示：「這場比賽肯定精采。不過無論我們遇上哪支球隊，都只會集中如何晉身下一圈。」<br />\n<br />\n日本跟南韓向來是世仇，但這名效力日職湘南比馬的中場卻示弱於人：「我認為南韓在體能及技術都比日本優勝，這場比賽肯定十分緊湊，極具娛樂性。若大家早知戰果，比賽就沒有趣味。」<br />\n<br />\n後衛瀬古步夢也認為，有華倫西亞李康仁組織的攻勢非常有威脅：「他們可能用很多高波，直接傳給前鋒，所以我們的中堅要能夠頂住壓力。」"},{"pid":"bf37462b197b7fdedb08090af1e8bec24670d78c","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:22:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vdr5PMB7S_A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dvdr5PMB7S_A&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=a5fc346a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vdr5PMB7S_A</a><br />\n中國俾愛爾蘭炒<br />\n土倫盃十幾場不勝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55022365a660ead5b00f06bef2cb816794f2cd2","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:13:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.vipstand.se/football-live-sports-stream\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vipstand.se%2Ffootball-live-sports-stream&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=90290402\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.vipstand.se/football-live-sport