es/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77915baeb9d5c6b99d1b8f66bea40135835de7ff","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T02:52:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RCE8BwJ-E_8?t=100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRCE8BwJ-E_8%3Ft%3D100&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=952ba23c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RCE8BwJ-E_8?t=100</a><br />\n精華"},{"pid":"8f4c8827a5aa5af7f55d47bdd2f6dc4b75ba3afb","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a519a67a02510a38be6d5a5356d3b49cbf2dd573","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T03:00:23.000Z","msg":"felix入大國腳<br />\n葡萄牙都喺熱門<br />\n不過炒十二碼出局 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T02:52:46.000Z","msg":"第一場歐國聯4強<br />\n佢就打正選"},{"pid":"ca3d3f6d9a40c688843455612424ce75d1092fd4","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:19:35.000Z","msg":"星期6晚2:30am<br />\n南韓8強會對塞內加爾"},{"pid":"d6f5ec2af6215d1163a5e7e59592bab617296ae3","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T04:47:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xx9ifL3IgsY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dxx9ifL3IgsY&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=3987347e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xx9ifL3IgsY</a><br />\n南韓98分鐘追平<br />\n加時領先又輸番球<br />\n互射十二碼入4強<br />\n峰迴路轉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe8d8545f969568431947ea628b4f0dadc15560","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:06:28.000Z","msg":"星期二晚2:30am<br />\n南韓會對厄瓜多爾"},{"pid":"d26d22f8aeda7bf7bf64dd35e817d7b5447fdb5d","tid":1181082,"uid":60916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:14:45.000Z","msg":"u20留力留到u30?"},{"pid":"3a20efd5859f05fea03458c01665b85338aae941","tid":1181082,"uid":80792,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:43:50.000Z","msg":"講到會死人咁"},{"pid":"67bff352120ce948259bf4aaa58f3b5ee5eddb18","tid":1181082,"uid":172226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"15153304d0bf80a735fa9658174521372549373c","tid":1181082,"uid":44349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d1c507504598287378db45505d2440afe43763db","tid":1181082,"uid":372,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"ad12ad114dcd05118e13dad0caaf1ef3b83e77b5","tid":1181082,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T10:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w71mFnr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw71mFnr.jpg&h=5daa5c42&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hq4GFns.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHq4GFns.jpg&h=8dba42ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在波蘭U20世界盃F組最後一輪比賽，南韓2：1擊敗阿根廷，近6屆5次晉級淘汰賽。將會於香港時間6月4日晚上11時30分與日本會師16強。<br />\n<br />\n其餘16強形勢是哥倫比亞對紐西蘭、烏克蘭對巴拿馬、意大利對波蘭、阿根廷對馬里、法國對美國、烏拉圭對厄瓜多爾和塞內加爾對尼日利亞。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙媒體評選賽事12位新星，有兩名亞洲球員上榜。沙特10號球員Turki Al-Ammar是沙特聯賽表現最好的球員之一。而南韓的李康仁也成功入選，他效力西甲球隊華倫西亞。 今年曾於聯賽及西班牙盃上陣；3月，他還入選有孫興慜領銜的大國腳。<br />\n<br />\n南韓對阿根廷憑李康仁左路傳中，中鋒吳世勳頭鎚領先1球。而下半場鄭洪金左路過人後傳中，曹永旭推射得手2-0。阿根廷6奪世青盃為歷隊最多。本場射門高達23次，南韓僅有7次。 最終有Adolfo Gaich追成1:2，小組兩勝一負排第1位。南韓力壓缺少賓菲加主力Joao Felix的葡萄牙排第2。 <br />\n<br />\n而日本在最後一輪0-0賽和意大利，小組第2出線。當中有18歲前鋒宮代大聖梅開二度大勝墨西哥。日本將力爭自03年再度晉級8強。<br />\n<br />\n早前日本公佈美洲盃名單，效力FC東京的久保建英首次入選大國腳，更成為史上第2年輕的一隊球員。主帥森保一明言有助對方成長。他今季聯賽入4球。早前有消息指，巴塞隆拿有意在他6月4日年屆18歲後重簽對方。<br />\n<br />\n早前中國於熊貓盃3戰全敗後，有球員說過：&ldquo;我們為保存實力才輸給南韓，畢竟我們基本功不差，與他們差距不大。這次沒有進世青盃，也是要保存實力而沒有去。&rdquo; 中國已經連續7屆無緣世青盃，上一次已是2005年。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T10:44:29.000Z","msg":"留足七年力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/